。

三泉修道院的歷史相當悠久。早在6世紀時，這裡已有紀念保羅的教堂<ref name="Tre Fontane">{{Cite_book
 |last        = Webb
 |first       = Matilda
 |title       = Abbazia delle Tre Fontane
 |publisher   = Sussex Academic Press
 |series      = The Churches and Catacombs of Early Christian Rome: A Comprehensive Guide
 |date        = 2001
 |url         = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=ESRnSBbNRGAC&pg=PA217&lpg=PA217&dq=San+Paolo+alle+Tre+Fontane+%225th+century%22+-wiki&source=bl&ots=qj-eatmA-R&sig=rWfpZ3Z-VWfpnmEkdexHKT-ibc0&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj20oS-g6rMAhUJopQKHaa-AgIQ6AEIKTAC#v=onepage&q=San%20Paolo%20alle%20Tre%20Fontane%20%225th%20century%22%20-wiki&f=false
 |isbn        = 978-1902210582
 |deadurl     = yes
