 |archivedate = 2016-05-07
 |access-date = 2016-05-02
}}</ref>。7世紀時，由於阿拉伯－拜占庭戰爭(另一說為由於[[基督一志論|基督一志論]]者的迫害<ref name="Abbey of Saints Vincent and Anastasius"></ref>)，一群來自小亞細亞的希臘僧侶帶著聖亞納大削的頭顱逃難至此，並建立起修道院。該院於13世紀在教宗[[洪諾留三世|洪諾留三世]]的指示下重建，並遷入[[聖味增爵|聖味增爵]]的遺體，改名為今稱─[[聖味增爵聖亞納大削修道院|聖味增爵聖亞納大削修道院]]<ref name="Tre Fontane"></ref>。而[[天階聖母堂|天階聖母堂]]與[[三泉聖保祿堂|三泉聖保祿堂]]則在16世紀經名建築師Giacomo della Porta重建<ref name= Rome >{{Cite_web
 | url = http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/13164a.htm
 | title = Rome
 | last = Umberto
 | first = Prat
 | date = 2016-05-03
 | website = New Advent
 | publisher = Robert Appleton Company
 | access-date = 2016-05-03
 | archive-date = 2020-11-26
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201126132106/https://www.newadvent.org/cathen/13164a.htm
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>
<ref name="Tre Fontane"></ref>。

西元1808，拿破崙軍隊入侵羅馬，僧侶逃離修道院，而修道院遭拿破崙軍隊洗劫<ref name="Official history">{{Cite_web
 | url = http://www.abbaziatrefontane.it/la-nostra-storia/
 | title = La nostra storia
 | website = Tre Fontane
 | access-date = 2016-05-03
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160421221204/http://www.abbaziatrefontane.it/la-nostra-storia/
 | archive-date = 2016-04-21
 | dead-url = yes
 }}</ref>。此後修道院一直處於荒廢狀態，並有嚴重的瘧疾問題，直到1867年在新任院長Milesi-Ferretti的積極修復，以及次年[[大特拉普聖母修道院|大特拉普聖母修道院]]派團前往，修道院才重新運作<ref name="Tre Fontane"></ref><ref name="Abbey of Saints Vincent and Anastasius"></ref>。但很快的在1870年，三泉修道院遭義大利政府強行充公，但院方堅守修道院，終於在1886年將修道院從政府買回。做為購買契約的一部份，修道院種植了大量的尤佳利葉做為對抗瘧疾的實驗，並取得一定的成功<ref name="Abbey of Saints Vincent and Anastasius"></ref>，而院方也利用了尤佳利葉做為其所生產的利口酒的特別成分 <ref name="Tre Fontane"></ref><ref name="Abbey of Saints Vincent and Anastasius"></ref><ref name= "the brewing monks">{{Cite_web
 | url = https://ithinkaboutbeer.com/2015/09/28/the-brewing-monks-the-11th-trappist-tre-fontane/
 | title = The Brewing Monks: The 11th Trappist – Tre Fontane
 | last = Barnes
 | first = Christopher
 | date = 2015-09-28
 | website = I think about beer
 | access-date = 2016-05-03
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324150438/http://ithinkaboutbeer.com/2015/09/28/the-brewing-monks-the-11th-trappist-tre-fontane/
 | archive-date = 2016-03-24
 | dead-url = yes
 }}</ref>。2014年，三泉修道院開始生產啤酒，並於2015年取得ATP認證，成為第11家擁有此認證的修道院啤酒廠<ref name= "the brewing monks"></ref>。

